	for USER in /etc/group.  Always include the one from /etc/passwd.
	* src/id.c (xgetgroups): Take new parameter, gid, and pass
	it to getugroups.
	(print_group_list): Call getpwuid and adjust calls to xgetgroups
	to include new parameter.
