	* src/chroot.c (usage): Add a `\' after `\n' in usage message.
	Otherwise, SunOS's /bin/cc chokes.

	* src/stty.c [GWINSZ_BROKEN]: Remove thus-guarded `#undef TIOCGWINSZ'.
	GWINSZ_BROKEN can't be defined anymore.

